@startuml
title Sequence Diagram (Alur Like dan Buat Post) - Aplikasi Sambat

actor User
participant "Browser / Frontend" as FE
participant "post_action.php" as PostAct
participant "like_action.php" as LikeAct
database "MySQL Database" as DB

== Skenario A: Membuat Postingan Baru ==
User -> FE : Tulis sambatan & klik "Sembur"
FE -> PostAct : POST (content_text, file_gambar)
PostAct -> DB : INSERT INTO posts
DB --> PostAct : Success / OK
PostAct -> FE : Redirect ke index.php
FE -> User : Tampilkan feed dengan post baru

== Skenario B: Like / Unlike Sambatan (AJAX) ==
User -> FE : Klik tombol Like (ikon hati)
FE -> LikeAct : Fetch API POST (post_id) (tanpa reload)
LikeAct -> DB : SELECT from likes WHERE post_id & user_id
DB --> LikeAct : Data ditemukan/tidak

alt Sudah pernah like
    LikeAct -> DB : DELETE FROM likes
else Belum pernah like
    LikeAct -> DB : INSERT INTO likes
end
DB --> LikeAct : Success / OK

LikeAct -> DB : SELECT COUNT(*) FROM likes WHERE post_id
DB --> LikeAct : total_likes
LikeAct --> FE : JSON { status: "success", action: "liked/unliked", total: N }
FE -> User : Update status ikon hati & angka like

@enduml
